{"id":62670,"date":"2021-08-31T13:26:13","date_gmt":"2021-08-31T12:26:13","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?p=62670"},"modified":"2021-12-18T19:18:00","modified_gmt":"2021-12-18T18:18:00","slug":"nice-things-to-do","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/nice-things-to-do\/","title":{"rendered":"7 Best Things To Do in Nice (French Riviera)"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"todo\">Things to do in Nice, France<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Nice is in an excellent location, sandwiched between the magnificent mountains of the Alps and the sparkling blue Mediterranean sea. It also sits close to the border of Italy, meaning you can easily visit on a day trip for your pizza fix! Spend mornings visiting bustling food markets, enjoy afternoons climbing to hillside viewpoints, and your evenings in beachside bars and bistros.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also visit:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/gorges-du-verdon\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Gorges du Verdon &#x2013; Most Beautiful Canyon in France<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27094730\/nice-france-2.jpg\" alt=\"nice france things to do\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"nice france things to do\" class=\"wp-image-63281 lazy