hair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31093930\/nice-france-23-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31093930\/nice-france-23-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31093930\/nice-france-23-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31093930\/nice-france-23-720x1080.jpg 720w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31093930\/nice-france-23-960x1440.jpg 960w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31093930\/nice-france-23-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31093930\/nice-france-23-600x900.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31093930\/nice-france-23.jpg 1280w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31093930\/nice-france-23-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31093930\/nice-france-23-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-climb-castle-hill\">Climb Castle Hill<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Castle Hill, or &#x2018;Colline du Chateau&#x2019;, is one of Nice, France&#x2019;s top things to do. The hill towers over the city, dividing it into two parts: the port and the old town. The castle itself was destroyed in 1706, but you can still see the ruins of the old defense walls, the cathedral, and other ancient buildings. Lots of greenery and flowers also surround an artificial waterfall (Cascade Dijon). This makes it a lovely place to relax and enjoy the incredible views over Nice.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotels-nice-france-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">See all the hotels to stay in the city.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27095134\/nice-france.jpg\" alt=\"nice france castle\"><\/noscript><img width=\"237\" height=\"338\" alt=\"nice france castle\" class=\"wp-image-63293 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1346px) 100vw, 1346px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27095134\/nice-france.jpg 1346w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27095134\/nice-france-421x600.jpg 421w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27095134\/nice-france-568x810.jpg 568w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27095134\/nice-france-237x338.jpg 237w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27095134\/nice-france-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27095134\/nice-france-114x163.jpg 114w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27095134\/nice-france-126x180.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\