rong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Did you know?<\/strong> Every day at 12 PM a cannon goes off from Castle Hill. The story goes that it was a signal from Sir Thomas Coventry-More (a former British military man) to his wife, asking her to come back for lunch. The tradition has continued for over 150 years!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31094712\/nice-france-24.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-63342 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31094712\/nice-france-24.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31094712\/nice-france-24-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31094712\/nice-france-24-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31094712\/nice-france-24-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31094712\/nice-france-24-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31094712\/nice-france-24-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31094712\/nice-france-24-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31094712\/nice-france-24-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31094712\/nice-france-24-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31094712\/nice-france-24-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31094712\/nice-france-24-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhai