\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Another popular thing to do in Nice <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/nice-wine-ebike-tour\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">is a vineyard e-bike tour with wine-tasting!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130834\/nice-france-8.jpg\" alt=\"nice france\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"nice france\" class=\"wp-image-63297 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130834\/nice-france-8.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130834\/nice-france-8-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130834\/nice-france-8-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130834\/nice-france-8-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130834\/nice-france-8-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130834\/nice-france-8-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130834\/nice-france-8-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130834\/nice-france-8-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130834\/nice-france-8-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130834\/nice-france-8-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130834\/nice-france-8-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/