/08\/27094805\/nice-france-5.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4><strong>La Reserve<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>La Reserve is east of the town, near the port area. It&#x2019;s secluded from the main city&#x2019;s busy areas, but it&#x2019;s small in size, so get there early to get a spot amongst the rocks. It&#x2019;s famous for great snorkeling and the old-fashioned diving boards just off the shore.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31091330\/nice-france-18.jpg\" alt=\"nice france beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"nice france beach\" class=\"wp-image-63328 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31091330\/nice-france-18.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31091330\/nice-france-18-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31091330\/nice-france-18-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31091330\/nice-france-18-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31091330\/nice-france-18-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31091330\/nice-france-18-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31091330\/nice-france-18-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31091330\/nice-france-18-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31091330\/nice-france-18-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31091330\/nic