y (travel guide)<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130846\/nice-france-9.jpg\" alt=\"nice france\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"nice france\" class=\"wp-image-63299 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130846\/nice-france-9.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130846\/nice-france-9-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130846\/nice-france-9-1080x720.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130846\/nice-france-9-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130846\/nice-france-9-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130846\/nice-france-9-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130846\/nice-france-9-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130846\/nice-france-9-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130846\/nice-france-9-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130846\/nice-france-9-1440x960.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130846\/nice-france-9-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130846\/nice-france-9-600x400.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130846\/nice-france-9-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130846\/nice-france-9.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-a-day-trip-to-menton\">A day trip to Menton<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Menton is a beautiful town, sitting east of Nice, right next to the border of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Italy<\/a>. The unique mix(ture) of the French and Italian culture makes for beautiful colored houses, palm tree avenues, luscious gardens, and Italian-style streets. It&#x2019;s no wonder <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/menton\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Menton<\/a> is called &#x2018;The Pearl of France&#x2019;. Spend a day here wandering the streets, taking photos, and enjoying delicious Italian food. Don&#x2019;t forget the gelato!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125402\/menton-france-17.jpg\" alt=\"menton france french riviera\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"menton france french riviera\" class=\"wp-image-63101 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125402\/menton-france-17.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125402\/menton-france-17-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125402\/menton-france-17-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125402\/menton-france-17-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125402\/menton-france-17-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125402\/menton-france-17-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125402\/menton-france-17-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125402\/menton-france-17-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125402\/menton-france-17-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125402\/menton-france-17-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125402\/menton-france-17-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125402\/menton-france-17-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125402\/menton-france-17-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125402\/menton-france-17-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125402\/menton-france-17.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Menton also has a unique microclimate, making it one of the sunniest spots in France. This means it&#x2019;s an excellent place for growing lemons. If you&#x2019;re visiting towards the end of February, check out the annual lemon festival of Menton &#x2013; a famous occasion in the French Riviera.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-583x810.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"243\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"63094\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/menton\/attachment\/menton-france-16\/\" class=\"wp-image-63094 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 583px) 100vw, 583px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-583x810.jpg 583w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-432x600.jpg 432w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-243x338.jpg 243w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-117x163.jpg 117w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-129x180.jpg 129w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-552x768.jpg 552w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-737x1024.jpg 737w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-777x1080.jpg 777w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-1036x1440.jp