eekly, where they sell delicious local Italian produce.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/menton\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Read all the Menton Travel Tips<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23084428\/menton-france-11.jpg\" alt=\"menton france\"><\/noscript><img width=\"438\" height=\"338\" alt=\"menton france\" class=\"wp-image-63078 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23084428\/menton-france-11.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23084428\/menton-france-11-777x600.jpg 777w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23084428\/menton-france-11-1049x810.jpg 1049w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23084428\/menton-france-11-438x338.jpg 438w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23084428\/menton-france-11-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23084428\/menton-france-11-163x126.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23084428\/menton-france-11-233x180.jpg 233w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23084428\/menton-france-11-768x593.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.salti