s to do\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"nice france things to do\" class=\"wp-image-63301 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130858\/nice-france-10.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130858\/nice-france-10-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130858\/nice-france-10-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130858\/nice-france-10-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130858\/nice-france-10-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130858\/nice-france-10-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130858\/nice-france-10-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130858\/nice-france-10-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130858\/nice-france-10-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130858\/nice-france-10-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130858\/nice-france-10-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130858\/nice-france-10-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130858\/nice-france-10-600x899.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130858\/nice-france-10-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27130858\/nice-france-10.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>When you&#x2019;ve finished at the beach, explore the charming old town of Villefranche-sur-Mer, stretching downhill to the sea. It&#x2019;s one of the only medieval towns that remain on this coastline, and it manages to retain its quaint charm despite being sandwiched between glitzy Nice and Monaco.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Visit on a&#xA0; Wednesday and a Saturday for the wonderful fresh food market that takes place halfway up the hill. Alternatively, there are plenty of amazing restaurants and pastry shops to choose from!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30133648\/nice-france-12-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"french riviera Villefranche sur Mer\"><\/noscript><img width=\"225\" height=\"338\" alt=\"french riviera Villefranche sur Mer\" data-id=\"63310\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30133648\/nice-france-12.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=