 one of the historic townhouses in the center, there are lots of great accommodation options to choose from in Nice. It&#x2019;s also a great jumping-off point to all the other charming seaside towns and villages in the French Riviera.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotels-nice-france-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">See all the hotels to stay in the city.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/nice-hotel-durante\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                    <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31130202\/hotel-durante-30x23.jpeg\" alt=\"Hotel Durante\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31130202\/hotel-durante-450x338.jpeg\">\n                    <div class=\"product__content\">\n                        <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                        <div class=\"product__content-title\">Hotel Durante<\/div>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        \n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a class=\"product__